To run the file, execute: 
>> make clean
>> make 
>> ./battleserver

Open a new terminal 
>> telnet localhost 30305
>> AnyNameOne

Open a new terminal
>> telnet localhost 30305 
>> AnyNameTwo


Use both terminals above to battle. 
Commands are: 
a => Normal attack
p => Power up attack (have limits to number of uses)
y => Allows you to send a message after and not miss a turn 

e.g. 
Client1: 
>> y
>> I win!
>> a
Client2:
>> p 
Client1: 
>> a
Continue battling till a client loses 

Note: You can keep repeating the command above to allow as many clients to battle each other as possible. 
 30305


